snippet.title: Epic War 3 Walkthrough - Cave of Trials 1 - Fire Demon
snippet.description:
This is a video of me, Tasselfoot, beating the 1st CoT level in Epic War 3.

Video is on 3x speed.

Game: http://www.kongregate.com/games/rudy_sudarto/epic-war-3?referrer=Tasselfoot

Music: Vivaldi's The Four Seasons - Winter.  http://www.musopen.com/music.php?type=piece&id=415
